Class MetaDataSerializer

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.querydsl.codegen.DefaultEntitySerializer
      • com.querydsl.sql.codegen.MetaDataSerializer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    EntitySerializer, Serializer

    public class MetaDataSerializer
extends DefaultEntitySerializer
    MetaDataSerializer defines the Query type serialization logic for MetaDataExporter. Extend this class for customization.

    tiwe
